data.description: Assume (with qualifying) 960,000 VA loan at 4.25% interest!!!  YOU DO NOT NEED TO BE A VET TO ASSUME THIS LOAN.  Beautifully renovated home in magic 85254 zip code.  Massive resort style backyard offering privacy, lush landscaping, on over a 10,000 sq. ft. lot.  Large pool and top of the line turf.  Home is light, bright, and open.  Tons of improvements over the past year - see list under Documents Tab. Some of the improvements include: custom closet, new irrigation lines, extended backyard outdoor patio and cover, epoxy paint on garage floor, painted kitchen cabinets and entire interior, $13,000 in sliding doors. This is an incredible home in an incredible location.  Floor plan makes the home seem much larger than square footage.
